main: ^Good day! I am Encarnacion Alzona, but you can call me Elly. I am currently here to learn about our own history. In my free time, I also love visiting bird sanctuaries because I really love birds!

c-0: ^That's cool. How many bird pets do you have?
^I have 12 birds and some of them are rescued.
^That's a lot. By the way, what program are you taking now?
^I am taking Bachelor of Science in Philosophy and History.
^That's great, Maybe I can ask you questions about the History of our country
^Sure! No problem. Just let me know if you think I can help you to know something.
